]

    clone_agent.context = {}  # independent memory
    clone_agent.preferred_output = staff["output"]
    
    # Integrate AI stack via SDK
    clone_agent.set_voice_input(WhisperInput())
    clone_agent.set_tts_output(ElevenLabsTTS(voice="office_ai"))
    clone_agent.set_file_handler([GoogleVisionOCR(), PyMuPDFHandler()])
    
    # Link agent to dashboard
    dashboard.register_agent(clone_agent)
    
    staff_agents[staff["name"]] = clone_agent
    logging.info(f"{clone_id} for {staff['name']} created and dashboard-linked.")

    # Convert voice notes to text

    # Extract text/content from files

        extracted_text = ""
        for handler in agent.file_handlers:
            extracted_text += handler.extract_text(message["media"])
        message["content"] = extracted_text

    # Decide output mode

        dashboard.send_to_inbox(agent.staff_id, reply_text, audio_file)

        whatsapp_notifier.send(error_msg)
